"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400 to-orange-500 text-white shadow-sm group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform\">★</div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm md:text-base group-hover:text-brand-600\">OBC / BC</h3><p class=\"text-slate-500 text-xs md:text-sm font-medium\">Backward Classes</p></div></a><a class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-slate-200/50 flex items-center gap-4 group\" href=\"/in?category=Minority\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-400 to-teal-500 text-white shadow-sm group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform\">★</div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm md:text-base group-hover:text-brand-600\">Minority</h3><p class=\"text-slate-500 text-xs md:text-sm font-medium\">Minority Communities</p></div></a><a class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-slate-200/50 flex items-center gap-4 group\" href=\"/in?category=Women\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-pink-400 to-rose-500 text-white shadow-sm group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform\">★</div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm md:text-base group-hover:text-brand-600\">Women</h3><p class=\"text-slate-500 text-xs md:text-sm font-medium\">Women &amp; Girls</p></div></a><a class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-slate-200/50 flex items-center gap-4 group\" href=\"/in?category=Students\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-400 to-fuchsia-500 text-white shadow-sm group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform\">★</div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm md:text-base group-hover:text-brand-600\">Students</h3><p class=\"text-slate-500 text-xs md:text-sm font-medium\">Scholarships &amp; Education</p></div></a><a class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-slate-200/50 flex items-center gap-4 group\" href=\"/in?category=Farmers\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-emerald-600 text-white shadow-sm group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform\">★</div><div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm md:text-base group-hover:text-brand-600\">Farmers</h3><p class=\"text-slate-500 text-xs md:text-sm font-medium\">Agriculture Schemes</p></div></a></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-white py-20 border-y border-slate-100 mb-20\"><div class=\"page-container\"><div class=\"text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-4\">How <span class=\"text-brand-500\">SchemeAtlas</span> Works</h2><p class=\"text-slate-500 text-lg\">We use AI to instantly match your exact social and financial profile to thousands of complex government rules.</p></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 relative\"><div class=\"hidden md:block absolute top-12 left-[15%] right-[15%] h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-100 via-brand-500 to-brand-100 z-0\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center\"><div class=\"w-24 h-24 bg-white border-4 border-slate-50 rounded-full shadow-xl shadow-brand-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-4xl mb-6\">📝</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">1. Tell us about you</h3><p class=\"text-slate-500 font-medium px-4\">Enter your age, caste category, state, and income. No personal info required.</p></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center\"><div class=\"w-24 h-24 bg-white border-4 border-slate-50 rounded-full shadow-xl shadow-brand-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-4xl mb-6\">🤖</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">2. AI Matching</h3><p class=\"text-slate-500 font-medium px-4\">Our AI engine scans 1000+ state and central schemes in 30 seconds.</p></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center\"><div class=\"w-24 h-24 bg-white border-4 border-slate-50 rounded-full shadow-xl shadow-brand-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-4xl mb-6\">🎯</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3\">3. Claim Benefits</h3><p class=\"text-slate-500 font-medium px-4\">Get exact links to official portals along with required document lists.</p></div></div></div></section></div><footer class=\"bg-slate-900 text-slate-400 py-12 border-t border-slate-800\"><div class=\"page-container text-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-6\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 bg-slate-800 rounded flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white font-bold text-xs\">C</span></div><span class=\"font-bold text-lg text-white\">SchemeAtlas</span></div><p class=\"text-sm mb-6 max-w-md mx-auto\">Not affiliated with any government entity. Data is aggregated from official sources (PIB, MyGov) and analyzed by AI for educational purposes.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-x-6 gap-y-3 px-4 text-sm font-medium mb-8\"><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/schemes\">Schemes</a><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/saved\">Saved</a><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/in/check\">Eligibility Checker</a></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500\"><a class=\"hover:text-slate-300 transition-colors\" href=\"/about\">About Us</a><a class=\"hover:text-slate-300 transition-colors\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"hover:text-slate-300 transition-colors\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a><a class=\"hover:text-slate-300 transition-colors\" href=\"/terms\">Terms of Service</a><a class=\"hover:text-slate-300 transition-colors\" href=\"/disclaimer